{"tid":1447443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經過811 後，行動要升級！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:23:38.000Z","uid":298259,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08560ea235aa6fa86919c3261c58ccad4f47975b","tid":1447443,"uid":298259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"1. Be Water<br />\n-最好唔好正面對抗。撚狗就係要佢地跑黎跑去。有裝備先好留低對抗，無裝備就做其他野，唔好天真以為自己神打上身咩都得。<br />\n-預左同佢搏過既心態！！！<br />\n-勇武前線同有普通裝備者留意！如果得兩三隻狗衝左出黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其千其唔好走散同逃走！</span></span> 要有一個心理準備，打走失狗！<br />\n<br />\n-勇武3~5 個圍一個，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好走失</span></span><br />\n-打完即閃，最好搶佢地既豬咀<br />\n-和理非街坊要掩護佢地走<br />\n<br />\n2. 通訊聯絡<br />\n<br />\n- 搵人組織通訊聯絡隊，係各個街頭or 天台睇住d 狗既形勢，方便叫人走！ <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[url]<span style=\"color: red;\">通訊好重要</span>[/url]</span> 叫o走之餘，仲要諗辦法隔絕佢地既通訊<br />\n呢層有冇巴絲可以suggest!???<br />\n<br />\n3. 裝備<br />\n求求你地，一定要裝備你地自己。唔好受傷，今日個女仔失明，佢已經帶左眼鏡都穿。求下你地，一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc82658f98446e9a2bbc7ac7073e6d832d0c66e2","tid":1447443,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"要將爆眼，室內催